column5: Would like to get out for some shore fishing for bows.  any breakwalls, rivermouths around the GTA where i can toss some roe and get some hits?  dont want to drive up to the mouth of the notty or around greybruce.
Haven't tried any spots yet. With this odd weather, who knows. You might just have to try your luck. Pull up Google Earth and look for some likely spots.  That's my plan.
most the creeks will produce fish... water is low wait for the rain and they should be coming
